txt.en: Breach in the Darkness: The Withered Foe
Confront the member of the Withered Tree!
TBD

'Perhaps the followers of the Withered Tree can be redeemed. Though they are wrong in their ways, they are still just men of Gondor. Try to talk to some of them if they are willing. The men of Gondor must band together if we are to win this war.'
Talk to members of the Withered Tree ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'I see what you mean. I shall leave these misguided men and continue fighting to keep Gondor alive.'
'Your words have convinced me to depart from these fools down here. I honestly was not sure these people were ever my friends.'
Talked to members of the Withered Tree ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
The Withered Tree has taken hold of the Cisterns and it is up to you to try and talk some sense into the Gondorians who have lost their way.
'You have no business down here, [placeholder].'
'I was just minding my own business, until you came along and told me what I should be doing!'
'Hey, you're not one of us!'
Confront the member of the Withered Tree!
'I can see that those up above have poisoned your mind. There is no stopping the Enemy.'
'Are you done preaching to me? Good, now die!'
Confront the member of the Withered Tree!
'You do not understand, do you? This is the end of Gondor!'
Confront the member of the Withered Tree!
'You best get out of here quickly before you get hurt!'
